this is more of a question post.  what should i do?

so i have orderd something from ebay. but seeins how i dont have a credit card i had to pay by cheque. so i put away the money i will need in my savings account so i cant touch it.  but tonite i went to check my account and the damn bank took out money from the Untouchable Savings account for a life insurance plan that i didnt even agree too!  i got a call asking if i wanted info on it and i said okay id like some info but i didnt sign up for that, i signed NOTHING. grr im soo mad.  what can i do???

So yea, i doubt anyone will read this, but i jsut felt like it was time to post again. 

hah i should probally look thru my old posts to see where i was at back then.

hahha omg thats sooo old! not much has changed, other then my jobs.  back then i was workin at SoftMoc, man that was alongago.  now i work at Bentley Leather. I sell luggage and purses whoohoo. lol  in a monthish i will start tryin to become assistant manager,  but lets do some bactrack.

from softmoc i went to lakeview market. was there about 6 months but i had my appendix out and after that they didnt give me many hours and then they made me choose work or family, so i quit on the spot.  was outta work for a bit, did a 3 day stint as a barrista at a friends coffee shop, but i dont think i could do that forever. then i was working at furry friends groomin parlour, i loved the animals but the co workers just werent nice to me or the animals. so i left.  so i was outta work for a while till i went to the mall, got the job at bentley and have been there since June. I like it there, they pay is lame but my manger and co workers ROCK! unfortunatly 2 of my super cool coworkers are leaving :( but hopefully they will visit.  i can train to become assistant manager after 3 months so thats kinda cool.  

other then work my life is pretty same ol same ol. still single. stil livin at home, new laptop (yay) and diffrent color hair, which will be changed agian on my next payday.  oh well i guess thats it, dinners ready so il post another time

thanks for reading

Michelle

shit now i need a new job.

well this is just a smidge overdue.  oh well not like anyone will read this. 

Well work was going well, keyword: was . Then came thanksgiving, i was supposed to have the day off but i got called in.  So it was a busy busy day and i was doing a million things at once, and i was in the back room gettin a box down and i fell off the ladder.  5 feet backwards off a ladder. so i landed on my left arm and my butt. I got up and told the manager, arm was horribly painful but i finsished the shift, then i had the next day off so i went to the doctor(walkinn) and he said to take a few days off. so i called my boss and told her this, she was notedly mad but oh well. so i was off and it still hurt, so i went to my family doctor and he was rather worried and sent me for xrays.  I also was told to take atleast a week off. so i called the boss and told her and she was mad but said okay. well the xrays came back on a monday and no break so i called to say i would be back on wednesday( lil less then a week later) so yea i went to work for light duty, Hah! what a joke. i was on my own for 4.5 hrs and while i was alone i did all the routine crap, pre pays, transfers, email checking, message checking and selling shoes and such,  anyway when scrolling thru the emails and i saw my name,  so as most people would do if they see there name on a Company all access computer.  So i read it and basically this is what it said  
mind you this is not quoted cuz i dont have the original

Hey Cheif, sorry to bother you with petty problems when you have much more important things to do. But Michelle called in again and supposedly her doctor told her to take more time off and for xrays, and if they are positive she wont be back for awhile.  my question to you is.  she has only been here 4-6 weeks maybe, so do i have any obligation to her or can i FIRE HER WHINEY ASS.   waiting to hear from you.   

so need less to say i was damn pissed off!  there were 3 emails like that all to her bosses.  so i worked out the day and pushed to hard and hurt bad.  so that nite i went home and called work and left a message saying that i would need more time off cuz it was just too much.  so the next morning she calls me up to get my BC Med Number cuz she was just then fillin out the workers comp forms ( i already had 3 forms from doctors in there) and at the end of the convo she said, "so you will call me when you can come back?" and i said "yes probally in a week"  so i thought all was okay untill today i get all these texts from my co worker saying i am not on the shedual and that i should call the boss to see if i was still employed there.  so i called WCB and asked there opinion and they said they hadnt recived the forms from the employer yet so they cant accept the claim yet.  so then i called my boss because i know they are damn swamped at work i called and said "Hi, its michelle, i was informed that i am not on the shedual for the next 2 weeks, if you still want me i can start again on LIGHT duty wednesday or thursday" she replied "umm, no thats okay, ill keep the shedual as is and you can call me on Nov. 3 to see when we can work ya in"  im sittin here like what the flying mother fucker???  but i kept my cool and finished the convo.  

If you havent guessed yet, i want to either quit or be fired from that mother fucking job but i cant because i am on WCB. GAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHHH

oh and also, i was hired there promised full time hours and training to be assistant manager, but for the few weeks befor the accident they cut my hours wayy down like maybe 50 per 2 weeks.  and i have gotten noo training for assistant manager, and then i saw that they have a ad up at guest services hiring a assistant manager,  ohh and when the head boss asshole was here he took both me and my co worker aside (btw we were told we were both the assistant manager) anyway when he took me aside he told me that he could see me with the company for alooong time and that he was tryin to get rid of the other girl and make me the sole assistant manager. so i was stoked for that.  and then the other day i was back to work the other girl and i were talkin and she said he had said the exact fucking thing to her too.   fuckin i hate people!!  

So ya, anyone wanna give me a job? heh, im find one soon i hope.  but i dont know if i can quit or be fired or what, so if anyone does read this, pleasse give me advice!!!!

okay well enuf for tonite,  buh bye

oh ya and i royally fucked up my knee tonite.  crap

Michelle

oh and to top it off my boyfried dumped me.  yay life

So my life has been basically uneventful,  thats probally why there has been no posts recently.

I worked 5 9 hr days in a row, and then i had 2 days off

It has been nice, hanging out with TJ more. shes a good friend.  We went to Timmys with a camera the other day, hehe.  

Yesterday i went on a first real date with James.  I think it went well. i wont go into details.  i was just coffee, movie, and moonlight beach walk.  

I only stayed out till 10pm last nite because i knew i was to work at 930 today. so i went to bed at about midnite. or so i thought.  
Except i didnt sleep. at all.  i tried to sleep and was laying there watching the hours tick by and then the room started to close in and i started shaking and long story short, i guess its what you would call a panic attack.  I dont know how or why i just know it was not cool.  so this morning  i called work, hoping to get the answeing machine. but gail (my boss) answered i told her what happened. and she said that she had my shift covered and to get some rest and figure out what is wrong. but i definetly have to go in to work tommorow. so i pray i can sleep tonite.

does anyone know why this would be happening to me?  well any help would be apreciated.  i think i will go get some food and maybe try to sleep now.
thanks for listening.
Michelle

well hmm what to say. oh ill start off saying HELL MONTH!!
we are really short staffed to begin with. and now this is just the rancid whipcream on the preverbial pie. here is a list of workers and there jobs.

okay, so long boring list  seems like a lot of workers right?  WRONG!  as of this week, Violet is on vacation, Inge is on vacation, Liz has been fired (still pissed about that, i am) and Candice is out on medical leave for at least a month. and Safeta is goin to summer college so she can only work 2 days a week.
soooooo.  we are down 4 and a half people.  and we are damn understaffed as it was.  So for cashiers there are 3 of us and we are all at the max hrs we can have.  I was damn sick the otherday but i couldnt go home because i was the only cashier! so it tottaly sucked!  and i have a friend who is in a play that i really wanna go see, but i never have the time cuz im almost always workin :( damn this fulltime stuff.

anyway,  what eles is new. hmmm  i went to the baseball game last week,  we lost. its weird every other time i have gone we have won, except this one. hmm.  
not much eles is happenin in my life.  ohh i have a creepy work story for ya

i was at work the other day (duh) and i was on Till One, which is the only till without a lil pull out shelf so that customers cant get into your area.  well ya One doesnt have it and i was havin a bad day, and all of a sudden this kid comes up INTO my area and starts running his fingers all over my back,  ohh frik man i wanted to slap him,   it was just aweful and creepy.  

so yea thats my story.  
ill let yall go now, i have bored you enough.

ta ta!

Mainly because there is nothing really to post. 
I work, come home, hang out. ya thats about it. 
I did buy myself a brand new kick ass laptop. its tottaly tubular dude. 

I thought I had something to say, but really i dont.

Wow,  I just had a vivid memory.  Sitting on Rachels porch off the family room up on Franklyn. Sitting there, at nite, wind blowing genally, the creepy fake owl hooting at nothing,  confrontation all around and the lonelyness over whelming. Thats how i feel theses days, sure i am around peopel most of the time, but the incredibal loneliness building inside me is unbearable.  

my birthday is in 19 days, i do not know what i want. oh well,  its just another passing year, big deal.

Evenin,  well actaully its mornin,  Easter mornin to be exact.

I hope all is well with all.  Nothing really new to report, i had saterday off and have sunday off, then its back to work till thursday and friday off. I have a staff meeting on wednesday, so that could be, interesting..  I have been told to start counting the change back to customers, but i just cant figure it out.  so i dunno how thats gunna go over. and ideas?

i finally got to hang out with an old friend last week,  it was great  brings back memories.  hopefully we can do it more.

so i turn the big one nine in a lil over a month,  and i have noo plans. its sad.

well this post was basically just for me to see how my new layout works, nothing of much significance in here, but when is there ever?

oh, does anyone know of a Rent-To-Own place that would rent laptops?  cuz i think i really want one, well i know i really want one but they are so damn expensive, so it be nice if i could try one for a month and see if i really do like it.  I also dont want to spend too much on it,  i found some online for under 900, so im lookin into that, one major thing is that i dont have a credit card so its hard to find how to pay online and such. 

okay, well thats all i really have to say,  i should get to bed, i have a feeling ill be up early for the easter stuff tommorow/today.

ttfn.  Michelle

well, i was informed that i havent updated in awhile.  so here is one.

so, i dropped off a resume on a friday,thinkin nothing would come of it. got a call for interview on monday, had an interview on tuesday, got a call i was hired on wednesday, started work on thursday.  
I work at Liquidation World,  not a very high class place, but the people seem nice, and hey, im making money. so whatever, its not permanent, just till i get some money and a better job.

So far i have worked 4 hrs on thursday, 6 hrs on friday, and tommorow well today now, i work 7 hrs. Really all i do is stock shelves, make sure everthing is in its place and price stuff. pretty damn boring. but occasionally i get called up to cashier assist. which is basically helpin the cashier by putting the items in bags and anything eles she needs.  In a few weeks i will be trained as a cashier, im almost wondering if i really want to be a cashier, cuz it can get rather stressfull and what im doin now is pretty slack.  It is nice to have a job where you are actually allowed to take a break, actually im supposed to take a 15 minute break after 2 hrs, if on a 4 hr shift, and a half hr break or 2 15 minute breaks. I am curious if i get 1 half hr break and a 15 min on a 8 hr.  I doubt that makes sence to anyone, too many numbers and such. 

anyyyyyyyyyyyyway  on to my personal life,  oh wait... i dont have one!  

i want to go swimmin!  maybe on my next day off i will. i hope so. ohh and sit in a hot tub, mmmmmm.
I have been gettin massages lately, because my friend is taking a massage course at the college, and she needs case studies. so that means free massages for me!  man i could use one right now.  

i am drinking hot choclate, but not just hot chocolate. Hot Chocolate with Vanilla, Chocolate and a smidge of Strawberry Ice Creams. yummm.  

I think my parents are going to buy me a carpet, cuz my room is just cement.  so that will be good. 

well, i think thats all i have to say for now.  
have a good rest of weekend everyone.

Michelle

i want to go swimming. 

i want a hottub.

i got a job.

i need new lipchap.

i want candles.

goodnite.

okay, so friday was my mums birthday, i shall not disclose the age because thats rude supposedly, even tho none of you know her, well thats not true, 2 of the 3 people who replied to my entry last nite actually know her, so hmm. if you have some strange fasination with my mums age, ask and ill tell ya. 

anyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyyy whoooooooooooom 

so my dad as some of you may know is a gardener/landscaper. He mainly works for really rich people around kelowna and the westside. anyway, he has this one client whom is very nice, and she lives in a really nice house with like 6 bedrooms and a hot tub and nice tv and such. she only lives there about 2 months of the year (a summer home if you will) since my dad has known her for awhile, and she knows we dont have alot of money, she told him that he could use her house as an occasional escape. instead of having to pay for a hotel or soemthing. anyway, it was moms b day, so they decided to take the lady up onm her offer and go there for the weekend. thus leaving us kiddies home alone for the 2 days. 

so they left on friday afternoon, and my lilest bro and sis (again if you know me you will know there names, and if you dont know me and know there names, ummmmm creepy) okay, so they were going to a campout/in with their youth group, so it would just be me and ryan and a empty house for the night (note ryan is my 23 year old brother, so get yur minds outta the gutter!! ewww) so yes, the afternoon of friday, mom and dad took us out for chinese food. my FAVORITE food.  so all was good and we were just about to order and we hear a boomsizzle!  and then the lights went out.  it was okay tho, because since we were the only people in the resturant at the time the cook cooked in the dark for us. okay so ya, we had a bunch of leftovers.   so friday for lunch i had chinese food and for dinner chinese food. 

So friday nite, home alone.  I would tell you about the amazingly radicallly awesome party we had,  only one problem.  we dodmnt have a party.  yep thats right,  i sat home, watching tv, playin computer games, drinkin hot chocolate, and talkin on the phone to my uncles who called, 3 diffrent ones, all drunk, to wish mom a happy b day. fuuun stuff!  hahah,  near 11 o clock i did have a Rum and Coke tho...   my bro and sister were supposed to call to check in, but never did, so i barely slept cuz i was to have the phone by my bed incase something happened and they called,  so i didnt sleep because i  am a deep sleeper, so if i was asleep and they called i wouldnt of heard it, so i didnt sleep, and they didnt call. 

note: i just realized that i have started almost every section with so.  yikes! isnt that like a rule not to do in english? heh sorry jordan.

so yea :P  saterday came and we had to go buy mom a gift, and have money left for pizza.  we went out and got her a nice bathset witha cute lil teddy, and still had money left for snacks,  when i say we i mean me and my bros and sis.  anyway, we went to the store and each got a bag of chips (mine is still unopened in my drawer) and each a bottle of pop.  and then i got a iced coffee and we came home. lisa and i started wrappin moms gift and the telephone rang, Mission Park Florists has a delivery for (insert moms name here)  so we waited around for them to come, 45 mins after theysaid they would be there.  so finally they came, and it was a really nice arangment but the card wasnt signed.  i was tempted to put my own name on it,  but i resisted.  so i had to figure what to do with these flowers, because since i have never recived flowers (Hint Hint!! *Cough Cough May 26 Cough Cough*)  so i just put them in some water still all nicely pakaged and took pictures of them, just incase i killed em befor mom got em (btw i didnt, they are still alive)  so then i wrapped moms gift all pretty like, and realized shit i forgot a card!  so id have to set up the printer and make one.   then the pizza came and i forgot aboot the card,  i have a new fav pizza tho. mmm canadaian!  after pizza i basically did nothing, well i cleaned, and then re cleaned. wahoo.  and at 1am, i remeberd i need a card! so i was up till about 3 am making a card. it was a damn nice card tho.  then i went to bed.  

okay, i know how boring this entry is, so ill spare you all and just finish a quick recap. 

sunday afternoon, parents came home, i went shopping with dad, and he bought me coffee. then we came home ate pizza and watched the Oscars, snoooooooooze.  then i just hung out and went to bed. 

monday,  took sister to waxin place, went to the store, dropped off resumes, came home, chatted online.  oh and the idiots across the street were using a bobcat thingy to do something in their front yard, and they hit a water line,  so there was a lil fountain for a bit.  the yard is still all dug up and shit.

alrite, well thats all for now,  sorry for boring you all. 

Michelle
